description:
Sometimes, I win. Sometimes, I lose. Through that I learn..

Learning to find the light within the dark has taught me to appreciate every little detail, life has to offer, good or bad, bitter or sweet, I can always learn from them and that's the best I could do..

A visual motion I made through the study of Perlin Noise and Flow Field.

